title: Shaman Active (&ltlvl 70)
comment_one:
Priority is "Quickness Boots" then dmg talents then "Lucky Clover" for more EXP gains.
*1 = As much as needed.
*2 = Put rest of points here.
comment_two: Go for 1 in each active skill, then you want "Power Overwhelming", "Individual Insight", "Knowledge is Power" and then "Unt'WIS'ted Robes".
comment_three:
Put ~30 points into "Virile Vials" (skip this part if you dont have many green vials.)
Go for 1 in each active skill, then you want to max "Earlier Education", after maxing it you can start adding more points to "Crazy Concotions"
notes: This is the end goal for around level 70, after that you want to invest into changes.
